## 🧠 Key Concepts Learned
- Infrustructure as a Server (IaaS) you have full control over operating system and application
- Platform as a Server (PaaS) you focus on building and developing application
- Software as a Server (SaaS) you use a complete application for example Gmail, or Zoom 

